***

43:24.930 --> 43:28.320
***

43:28.370 --> 43:33.000
* I'll take my time

43:33.040 --> 43:35.270
* And I'll take my chances

43:35.310 --> 43:37.870
* I'm gonna find you

43:37.910 --> 43:41.243
* As long as
I'm still standing *

